What is this

Small app using Sinatra and ruby-readability to make web articles easier to read when displaying in mobile apps.

Usage

URL: http://readable.heroku.com/read/{url_to_be_read}

Example: http://readable.heroku.com/read/http://www.cnn.com/2011/CRIME/03/05/connecticut.east.coast.rapist/index.html?hpt=T1
